<center><H1>Pick of the Week</H1></center>

<P>
<P align=center><I>Top stories from the September 21, 1996, issue of Chemist &amp; Druggist
Newsweekly</I></P>

<P>
<A HREF="#a">Unease over new script software</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#b">Patience required for packs</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#c">CPG launches Gatekeeper initiative</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#d">Needle exchange threatened</A>
<P>
