<BODY>

<P>
 

<P align=center><IMG SRC="gifs/logosm.gif" ALT="dotPHARMACY logo"> 
<H1><P align=center>Jobs of the Week</center></H1>

<P>
<I><P align=center>A selection of opportunities from the Classified section of
this week's Chemist &amp; Druggist</CENTER> </I>
<P>
<P align=center>To book space, 'phone Claire Wilkins or James Whitson on 01732 377310, fax on 01732
