 <IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE SRC="geo/images/coe.gif">  <P>
 <H1> USACE HEADQUARTERS DATA PAGE </H1>

 <IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE SRC="geo/images/thin-bar.gif">
 <P>

 <H2>
 <IMG ALIGN=bottom SRC="geo/images/3d2.gif"> 
National Inventory of Dams <P> </H2>
<H3>
<UL> 
<LI><A HREF="ftp://corps_geo1.usace.army.mil/headquarters/metadata/dam-inv.met"> 
Metadata </A>  </H3> 
 

<H3><LI> <A HREF="ftp://corps_geo1.usace.army.mil/headquarters/geo_data/damdata"> Online Dataset  </A>  <IMG SRC="/images/new.gif"> </H3>
 We now have a complete copy of the 1995-96 revised National 
Inventory of Dams CD-ROM available online.  The data are presented in comma 
delimited ASCII, dBase III, and Paradox 3.5 formats and are available by 
state and NID. 
</UL> 
 <HR>

<H2>
<IMG ALIGN=bottom SRC="geo/images/castle.5.gif">
USACE District/Division Boundaries <P> </H2>
