<TITLE>USA Corps of Engineers National Geospatial Data Clearinghouse Site </TITLE>
</head>

<body>

<H3> National Spatial Data Infrastructure</H3>

<h3> National Geospatial Data Clearinghouse Node</h3>

<h3> US Army Corps of Engineers</h3>

 <a href = "http://www.usace.army.mil">
 <img src = "geo/images/usace.gif" alt = "USACE Home Page"> </a>
 <img src = "geo/images/gray.gif" alt = "Invisible color bar">
 <a href = "http://fgdc.er.usgs.gov/nsdi2.html">
 <img src = "geo/images/ansdi1x1.gif" alt = "NSDI logo"> </a>
 <HR>
 <P>
 
Welcome to the U.S. Army Corps of Engineers node of the National Geospatial Data Clearinghouse, a component of the National Spatial Data Infrastructure (NSDI).
<p> 
<h3>Table of Contents</h3>
 <H3> <IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM SRC="geo/images/purpledot.gif"> USACE Policy, Procedures, and General Information</H3> <P>
 <ul>
 <li>  <A HREF="ftp://corps_geo1.usace.army.mil/pub/er8156">ER 1110-1-8156  </A> (ER 1110-1-8156 supercedes EC 1110-1-83) (Word Perfect 6.1 format)

<li>  <A HREF="ftp://corps_geo1.usace.army.mil/pub/em2909">EM 1110-1-2909 </A>
Engineer Manual (Word Perfect 6.1 format)

<li> <A HREF="ftp://corps_geo1.usace.army.mil/pub/survey"> 1994 USACE GD&S survey  </A>  (MS Excel format)

<li> <A HREF="ftp://corps_geo1.usace.army.mil/pub/gd_and_s">GD&S POCS </A> for each
USACE command (Word Perfect 6.1 format) 

</ul>

<H3> <IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM SRC="geo/images/redball.gif"> METADATA  </H3> </A>
<UL>
<LI> <a href = "howto/how-to.html">
USACE Geospatial Data Server: Manual on
how to submit and access data and metadata</a> - Version 22 Nov 96
<img src = "../images/updated.gif" align = bottom> 

<LI> <a href="metadata.html"> Locating USACE Metadata using maps  </a>

