USACE Commands </a>

<LI>  <A
HREF="http://corps_geo1.usace.army.mil/geo/query.html"> Search USACE and
NSDI Clearinghouse metadata databases using a form    </a> 

<li>  <A HREF="ftp://corps_geo1.usace.army.mil/pub/corpsmet_v2.x/">CORPSMET </A> Metadata Generation Software <IMG Align=BOTTOM SRC="./images/new.gif">
<ul> The latest version of Corpsmet has been released!  The newest version is 2.03.
Click on the above link to download it.
</ul>

</UL>
