 <HTML>
 <HEAD>
 <TITLE>Summary Matrix of Geographic Information Systems Activities </TITLE>
 </HEAD>
 <BODY>
 <H1>Summary Matrix of Geographic Information Systems activities in the U.S. 
	Army Corps of Engineers Research and Development Laboratories <P> </H1>
 <H3>
The Matrix has been compiled by Penny Capps at HQ USACE.  It summarizes the 
planned GIS activities for FY96 for the Corps of Engineers R&D Laboratories.
It is available in several word processing formats, please choose the one most 
appropriate for your operating environment. <P> </H3>

 <H4>
Available Formats: </H4>
 <ul> <ul>
 <A HREF="ftp://corps_geo1.usace.army.mil/pub/summary/f96mat.wp6">
	Word Perfect 6.1 </A> <P>

 <A HREF="ftp://corps_geo1.usace.army.mil/pub/summary/f96mat.wp5">
	Word Perfect 5.0  </A> <P>

 <A HREF="ftp://corps_geo1.usace.army.mil/pub/summary/f96mat6.doc">
	Microsoft Word 6.0 </A> <P>

 <A HREF="ftp://corps_geo1.usace.army.mil/pub/summary/f96mat5.doc">
	Microsoft Word 2 </A> <P>


 </BODY>
 </HTML>
