<HEAD>
<TITLE>Corps_geo1 user-id request instructions</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY>
<H1>CORPS_GEO1 USER-ID REQUEST INSTRUCTIONS</H1>
<H2> To gain access to the USACE Geospatial Metadata and Data Server (Corps_geo1) to submit metadata and data you need to do 2 things:</H2>

<NL>
<LI> Submit your name, email address and USACE organization to the Corps_geo1 webmaster.  You can do this one of three ways:
    <UL>
    <LI>Via our web <A HREF="user-id2.html">form</A>
    <LI>email <A HREF="mailto:webmaster@corps_geo1.usace.army.mil">webmaster@corps_geo1.usace.army.mil</A>
    <LI>Phone Chad Adams at (603) 646-4320
    </UL>
<LI> You must also have your UPASS administrator make a UPASS request for an account for you on the Geospatial Metadata and Data Server on Corps_geo1.  If they have any difficulties they should contact the Webmaster at the email address or phone number listed above.
</NL>
<P>
<I>PLEASE NOTE:</I>  Without your email address we can <strong>NOT</strong> process your UPASS request.  It will be held until your email address is received.
<P>

Thank you for your cooperation.

</BODY>
