 <HTML>
 <TITLE>FEDERAL GEOGRAPHIC DATA COMMITTEE </TITLE>

 <H1>FACILITIES WORKING GROUP HOME PAGE </H1>

 <BODY>
 <H3>The Next Meeting is 10 Feb 1997 1:00 - 3:00<p> </H3>


 <H3>Location: <br>   
Room 8222D
<A HREF="pulaski.html">Pulaski Building</A>, HQUSACE <br>
20 Massachusetts Avenue, NW <br>
Washington, DC 20314-1000 <br> </H3>


 <H3>Agenda: <P></H3>
<H4>
The major topics for this meeting are the development of a Facility ID standard, utility data content standard, an environmental hazard data content standard, and an accuracy standard for facility mapping.
 </H4>
 <HR>
<H3>Additional Project Team Meetings:<P></H3>
<H4>January 13, 1997 - Room 7123C, Pulaski Building
	<UL><LI>9:00 - 12:00 Facility ID and Environmental Hazards Standards Team</LI>
	<LI>1:00 - 4:00 Utilities Standard Team</LI></UL>
February 10, 1997 - Room 8124C, Pulaski Building
        <UL><LI>9:00 - 12:00 Facility ID and Environmental Hazards Standards</LI>
	<LI>3:15 - 4:15 Utilities Standard Team</LI></UL>
March 10, 1997 - Room 7123C, Pulaski Building
        <UL><LI>9:00 - 12:00 Facility ID and Environmental Hazards Standards</LI>
	<LI>1:00 - 4:00 Utilities Standard Team</LI></UL>
</H4>
<HR>
 <H4> <A HREF="http://fgdc.er.usgs.gov/fgdc.html">Return to FGDC Home Page </A> </H4> <p>

 <H4> <A HREF="../welcome.html">Return to USACE Geospatial Clearinghouse Title Page </A> </H4> <P>
 <HR>
Page owner:  <a href = "mailto:webmaster@corps_geo1.usace.army.mil">
webmaster@corps_geo1.usace.army.mil </a> <p>
