        <td width="50%"> 
        <h1><u>The Electronic Library</u> </h1>
        </td>
        <td width="50%"> 
        <p align="center"><img src="images/library_.gif"
        align="bottom" width="62" height="64"> </p>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
<p>&#160; </p>
<p>Welcome to the Corning Pharmaceutical Services Electronic
Library. In this library we intend to offer information and
articles written by CPS employees providing information about new
and existing technologies at work within CPS. If you require any
further information on these articles or any others please
contact <a href="mailto:sthomas@corningb.co.uk">sthomas@corningb.co.uk</a>
or reply via our <a href="FEEDBACK.HTM">feedback </a>form.</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
<table width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td width="10%"><img src="images/cardfile.gif"
        align="bottom" width="113" height="150"></td>
        <td width="50%">If you are looking for something
        specific, please use our search facility:
        <form action="_vti_bin/shtml.exe/library.htm"
        method="POST">
            <input type="hidden" name="VTI-GROUP" value="0">
            <p><b>Search for: </b><input type="text"
            name="search" size="20" value></p>
            <p><input type="submit" value="Start Search"><input
            type="reset" value="Reset"></p>
        </form>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
