    <dd><a href="medwrit.htm">Medical Writing</a> - Reports
        dispatched to clients in 1995</dd>
    <dd><a href="library.htm">Electronic Library</a> - Managed
        Care- what does it mean?</dd>
    <dd><a href="library.htm">Electronic Library</a> -
        Biotechnology articles</dd>
