<h1 align="center"><img src="images/cps2.gif" align="bottom"
width="306" height="45"></h1>
<h1 align="center"><u>Career Opportunities</u></h1>
<p>Corning Besselaar is one of the largest world-wide Clinical
Research Organisations performing clinical research for the
pharmaceutical industry. We are part of a multinational
corporation, <a href="cps.htm">Corning Pharmaceutical Services</a>.</p>
<p>We offer a competitive salary and a first class benefits
package, bonus, non contributory pension scheme and free medical
insurance (after a short qualifying period)</p>
<p>We welcome speculative CVs for all vacancies within the
organisation.</p>
<p>Due to expansion, we currently offer a variety of vacancies
based at our offices in Maidenhead, Berkshire UK, as well as most
of our other European offices.</p>
<p>You can also view the full range of International Vacancies at <a
href="http://www.corningps.com">http://www.corningps.com</a></p>
<p><a href="clinical.htm"><strong>CLINICAL</strong></a></p>
<ul>
    <li>Clinical Research Manager</li>
    <li>Clinical Research Associate</li>
    <li>Senior Clinical Research Associate</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="opportun.htm"><strong>EDMC</strong></a></p>
<ul>
    <li>Clinical Data Manager</li>
    <li>Data Entry Operator</li>
    <li>Data Technician</li>
    <li>Statistician</li>
    <li>Statistical Programmer</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="BDopps.htm"><strong>BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT</strong></a></p>
<ul>
    <li>Senior Business Development Associate</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="reg.htm"><strong>REGULATORY AFFAIRS</strong></a></p>
<ul>
    <li>Clinical Quality Assurance Auditor</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="infoser.htm"><strong>INFORMATION SERVICES</strong></a></p>
<ul>
    <li>Senior Analyst Programmer</li>
    <li>Analyst Programmer</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="Genvac.htm"><strong><u>GENERAL</u></strong></a></p>
<ul>
    <li>European Accounting Manager</li>
</ul>
<p>If you are interested in joining our rapidly expanding
organisation, please forward your Curriculum Vitae to:</p>
<dl>
    <dd>Amy Hulme </dd>
    <dd>Human Resources Department</dd>
    <dd>Corning Besselaar Limited</dd>
    <dd>7 Roxborough Way</dd>
    <dd>Maidenhead, Berkshire SL6 3UD</dd>
    <dd>United Kingdom.</dd>
    <dd>&#160;</dd>
    <dd>e-mail: <a href="mailto:sthomas@corningb.co.uk">sthomas@corningb.co.uk</a></dd>
</dl>
<p><strong>(Please mark applications: INTERNET)</strong></p>
