<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3O/DTD HTML//EN">

<html>
<head>
<title>Corning Pharmaceutical Services</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif">
<h1 align="center"><MAP NAME="FrontPageMap"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="3, 0, 103, 35" HREF="index.htm"><AREA COORDS="0,0,10000,10000" HREF="index.htm"></MAP><a href="/corningb/_vti_map/cps.htm.map"><img
align="bottom" src="images/home.gif" width="104" ismap
usemap="#FrontPageMap" height="38" border="0"></a></h1>
<h1 align="center"><img src="images/cps2.gif" align="bottom"
width="306" height="45"></h1>
<h1 align="center"><img src="IMAGES/aniglobe.gif" align="bottom"
width="39" height="42"></h1>
<p>Corning Pharmaceutical Services brings together the combined
experience and capabilities of the worlds leading companies in
each stage of pharmaceutical and biotechnology <a href="ddc.htm">drug
development</a>. The Corning Pharmaceutical Services network is
comprised of six world-class industry leaders:</p>
<h4><MAP NAME="FrontPageMap1"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="1, 2, 158, 12" HREF="hazel.htm"></MAP><a href="/corningb/_vti_map/cps.htm.1.map"><img
align="bottom" src="images/hazelton.gif" width="159" ismap
usemap="#FrontPageMap1" height="13" border="0"></a><br>
World's leader in nonclinical safety assessment and drug
disposition</h4>
<h4><MAP NAME="FrontPageMap2"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="4, 0, 143, 12" HREF="http://www.bio.com/home/corning/scicor.html"></MAP><a href="/corningb/_vti_map/cps.htm.2.map"><img
align="bottom" src="images/scicor.gif" width="144" ismap
usemap="#FrontPageMap2" height="13" border="0"></a><br>
World's leading centralised clinical laboratory devoted
exclusively to pharmaceutical studies</h4>
<h4><MAP NAME="FrontPageMap3"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="1, 1, 159, 12" HREF="intro.htm"></MAP><a href="/corningb/_vti_map/cps.htm.3.map"><img
align="bottom" src="images/bess.gif" width="160" ismap
usemap="#FrontPageMap3" height="13" border="0"></a><br>
World's leading clinical contract research organisation
experienced in both national and multinational development
programs</h4>
<h4><MAP NAME="FrontPageMap4"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="1, 0, 137, 12" HREF="pact.htm"></MAP><a href="/corningb/_vti_map/cps.htm.4.map"><img
align="bottom" src="images/pact.gif" width="138" ismap
usemap="#FrontPageMap4" height="13" border="0"></a><br>
World's leading specialist in designing and conducting large
scale and specialised periapproval studies</h4>
<h4><MAP NAME="FrontPageMap5"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="1, 0, 115, 12" HREF="http://www.bio.com/home/corning/bio.html"></MAP><a href="/corningb/_vti_map/cps.htm.5.map"><img
align="bottom" src="images/bio.gif" width="116" ismap
usemap="#FrontPageMap5" height="13" border="0"></a><br>
World-class outsourced CGMP i-manufacturing services to the
biopharmaceutical community</h4>
<h4><MAP NAME="FrontPageMap6"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="0, 1, 164, 29" HREF="http://www.bio.com/home/corning/natpack.html"></MAP><a href="/corningb/_vti_map/cps.htm.6.map"><img
align="bottom" src="images/natpack.gif" width="165" ismap
usemap="#FrontPageMap6" height="30" border="0"></a><br>
World-class full-service contract packager registered with the
FDA and the DEA</h4>
<p>As a global resource, the Corning Pharmaceutical Services
network of companies can handle all aspects of the <a
href="ddc.htm">drug development cycle </a>from preclinical
through clinical and periapproval studies, all the way to
contract manufacturing, packaging and labelling.</p>
<p>Being a part of <a href="http://www.corning.com">Corning
Incorporated</a> is very important to Corning Pharmaceutical
Services. Corning provides the investment to develop new
businesses, such as Corning Bio, Corning HTA and <a
href="http://bio.com/home/corning/natpack.html">Corning National
Packaging</a>, and new technology to provide customers with even
broader and more efficient <a href="ddc.htm">drug development</a>.
This new technology has already resulted in:</p>
<ul>
    <li>State-of-the-art medical imaging techniques</li>
    <li>Proprietary data management systems</li>
    <li><a href="ias.htm">On-line customer communication and
        information access</a></li>
    <li><a href="ivrs.htm">Interactive voice response systems</a>
        (IVRS)</li>
</ul>
<p>ANNUALLY, CORNING PHARMACEUTICAL SERVICES PERFORMS:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Over 600 toxicology studies</li>
    <li>180 Phase I studies</li>
    <li>100 Phase II - IV studies</li>
    <li>Clinical packaging for more than 300 studies</li>
    <li>Central laboratory testing for more than 900 clinical
        trials</li>
    <li>More biopharmaceutical assays than anyone else in the
        world</li>
</ul>
<p>No other developmental organisation offers the global
experience, breadth of services, and financial stability
available through these world-class companies.</p>
<ul>
    <li><a href="hazel.htm">Corning Hazleton</a></li>
    <li><a href="http://www.bio.com/home/corning/scicor.html">Corning
        SciCor</a></li>
    <li><a href="intro.htm">Corning Besselaar </a></li>
    <li><a href="pact.htm">Corning PACT </a></li>
    <li><a href="http://www.bio.com/home/corning/bio.html">Corning
        Bio</a> </li>
    <li><a href="http://www.bio.com/home/corning/natpack.html">Corning
        National Packaging</a></li>
    <li>Corning HTA</li>
</ul>
<h4>Today, whenever you need to outsource drug development, you
can pick and choose one or more or all of us.</h4>
<h4>Remember, you will be choosing:</h4>
<h3><img src="images/dot.gif" align="texttop" width="31"
height="31"> The financial stability of a Fortune 500 company</h3>
