<title>Phase I Clinical Research Unit Leeds</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif">
<p align="center"><MAP NAME="FrontPageMap"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="5, 2, 103, 37" HREF="index.htm"></MAP><a href="/corningb/_vti_map/phasei.htm.map"><img
align="bottom" src="images/home.gif" width="104" ismap
usemap="#FrontPageMap" height="38" border="0"></a></p>
<p align="center"><img src="images/logo.gif" align="bottom"
width="363" height="31"></p>
<h2><a href="http://www.corningbesselaar.co.uk">Phase I Europe</a></h2>
<p>The 60 bedded<a href="http://www.corningbesselaar.co.uk">
Phase I Unit in Leeds</a> provides extensive facilities and
capabilities to examine early clinical safety, tolerability,
pharmacokinetics and pharmacodynamics of candidate medicines.</p>
<p>With in-house expertise from pharmacists, physicians, nursing
and scientific and technical personnel we have the support
available to assist with clients clinical development plans.</p>
<p>With in excess of 70 clinical Phase I studies conducted
annually in Leeds and over 9 years experience, together with
being awarded the <a href="iso9001.htm">BS EN ISO 9001</a>
Quality Award the facilities are regarded as being one of the
&#147;top&#148; clinics in Europe for placement of studies by
client companies. </p>
<p>Additional services located in Leeds include data management
and regulatory groups. These together with the links with the
pre-clinical toxicology departments at Corning Hazleton and our <a
href="phaseii.htm">Phase II </a>colleagues have enabled us to
assist in the &#147;<a href="fastrak.htm">fast tracking</a>&#148;
of <a href="ddc.htm">drug development</a> from pre-clinical to
early efficacy trials in patients.</p>
<p><MAP NAME="FrontPageMap1"><AREA SHAPE="CIRCLE" COORDS="41, 38, 38" HREF="iso9001.htm"></MAP><a href="/corningb/_vti_map/phasei.htm.1.map"><img
align="bottom" src="images/bsi.gif" width="80" ismap
usemap="#FrontPageMap1" height="77" border="0"></a> A <a
href="iso9001.htm">BS EN ISO 9001</a> accredited company.</p>
<h3><a href="http://www.corningbesselaar.co.uk">More information</a></h3>
