<html>
<head>
<title>The European Data Management Centre</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<p align="center"><a href="index.htm"><b><img
src="images/home.gif" align="bottom" border="0" width="104"
height="38"></b></a></p>
<p align="center"><img src="images/logo.gif"
alt="Corning Besselaar" align="bottom" width="363" height="31"></p>
<h1 align="center"><strong>The European Biostatistics and Data
Management Centre (EDMC)</strong></h1>
<h2 align="center"><em>Leading the way throughout Europe</em></h2>
<p><b><u>Europe's Leading Data Centre</u></b><u> </u></p>
<p>In 1990, Corning Besselaar created the EDMC in Maidenhead,
U.K. This <a href="Technol.htm">state-of-the-art</a> facility
offers the client the opportunity to work closely with contract
data management and statistical personnel processing clinical
research data. EDMC utilises Wide Area Networks which support
Paradox, Clintrial and Sybase databases and using SAS-based
diagnostics and reporting systems.</p>
<p>The qualified EDMC professional staff also work hand-in-hand
with Corning Besselaar's clinical research offices throughout
Europe to process and analyse data from Corning
Besselaar-monitored studies quickly and efficiently. </p>
<p>EDMC provides a valuable supplementary resource for managing
your data from national and international clinical programmes.
Working in tandem with Corning Besselaar's data management
facilities in the US, EDMC offers you the opportunity to handle
data on a global scale. </p>
<p><a href="edmc1.htm"><b><u>Choose the services that you require</u></b></a></p>
<p>Successful partnerships are built on compatibility - listening
to the clients needs and fulfilling them. EDMC works as a
seamless extension of the clients staff, providing the services
they <a href="edmc1.htm">require</a> and following their in-house
procedures, documentation and guidelines. </p>
<p>Or, you can confidently rely on EDMC to handle your specific
project with our approach to personalised service and the high
standards of EDMC's operating procedures. From original case
report forms and analysis plans to a final database, statistics
and report writing, whatever you require, we will meet or exceed
your expectations. </p>
<p><b><u>People Are The Key</u></b><u> </u></p>
<p>Even the most advanced data management system is only as good
as the people who make it work. </p>
<p>EDMC staff include academically qualified statisticians,
specialist statistical programmers and systems experts, and
highly trained data managers. A dedicated Quality Assurance
Department provides support. </p>
<p>An EDMC professional is assigned to each study as the Project
Coordinator responsible for every stage and for keeping the
client informed. </p>
<p><b><u>Unsurpassed Quality Of Service</u></b><u> </u></p>
<p>At EDMC, quality principles form the basis of everything we
do. </p>
<p>Quality Control checks are integral to each stage of
processing from the initial data review to the final database and
reports generated from it. Computer programs and statistical
analyses are reviewed and validated. </p>
<p><a href="regulato.htm">Quality Assurance</a> and regular
review of databases and reports further guarantee that standards
are maintained. Audit certificates are provided with each final
report. </p>
<p><MAP NAME="FrontPageMap"><AREA SHAPE="CIRCLE" COORDS="41, 37, 37" HREF="iso9001.htm"></MAP><a href="/corningb/_vti_map/edmc.htm.map"><img align="bottom"
src="images/bsi.gif" width="80" ismap usemap="#FrontPageMap"
height="77" border="0"></a></p>
<p><a href="iso9001.htm">BS EN ISO 9001</a> Accredited Company.</p>
<p>EDMC is a centre of excellence. One of our recent initiatives
has been the recent certification of EDMC to the <a
href="iso9001.htm">BS EN ISO9001</a> standard. EDMC is the only
European standalone data management centre which has attained
this standard.</p>
