<html>
<head>
<title>Information Access System</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Vermeer FrontPage 1.0">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif">
<p align="center"><MAP NAME="FrontPageMap"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="2, 0, 103, 37" HREF="index.htm"></MAP><a href="/corningb/_vti_map/ias.htm.map"><img
align="bottom" src="images/home.gif" width="104" ismap
usemap="#FrontPageMap" height="38" border="0"></a></p>
<h1><u>Information Access System (IAS)</u></h1>
<h2>&quot;A Window On Your Project&quot;</h2>
<p>IAS is an innovative clinical development technology that
continuously integrates key study data across the <a
href="cps.htm">Corning Pharmaceutical Services</a> network.
Running on Lotus Notes, &quot;The Groupware Standard&quot;, IAS
offers clients round-the-clock access to data such as patient
enrolment, laboratory visit information, trip reports, serious
adverse events, CRF status, as well as project financial status.
IAS enhances communication and helps to streamline project
management.</p>
<ul>
    <li>Facilitates project planning and control especially
        critical in large multinational studies. Produces direct
        time/cost savings in clinical trial management.</li>
    <li>Reduces monitoring costs by optimizing visit schedules
        based on actual patient enrolment.</li>
    <li>Speeds up communication through client-dedicated,
        confidential E-mail link.</li>
    <li>Allows for continuous communication resulting in
        proactive project management.</li>
    <li>Keeps you, the sponsor, in control.</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<p align="center"><MAP NAME="FrontPageMap1"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="459, 7, 543, 103" HREF="http://sthomas.technocom.com/CBE2/library.htm"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="368, 7, 452, 103" HREF="http://sthomas.technocom.com/CBE2/library.htm"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="278, 7, 363, 103" HREF="cps.htm"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="187, 7, 272, 103" HREF="caropps.htm"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="97, 7, 182, 103" HREF="contact.htm"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="6, 7, 92, 103" HREF="index.htm"><AREA COORDS="0,0,10000,10000" HREF="index.htm"></MAP><a href="/corningb/_vti_map/ias.htm.1.map"><img
