<DOCNO>WT16-B27-205</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA078-000532-B039-268</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.corningbesselaar.com:80/ivrs.htm 194.6.96.221 19970211032742 text/html 4239
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Tue, 11 Feb 1997 03:30:02 GMT
