<h3><a name="Senior Business Development Associate "><strong><u>Senior
Business Development Associate </u></strong></a></h3>
<p>The primary role for this position will be to develop and
increase the revenue for a Business Unit through proactive
account management and sales activities for specified clients.</p>
<p>Responsibilities will involve the development and ongoing
monitoring of account plans and sales forecasts, managing
existing accounts and clients services to ensure customer
satisfaction. You will also be responsible for the production and
development and delivery of proposals including presentations to
existing clients.</p>
<p>The ideal candidate will have four or more years in the
pharmaceutical industry with at least 2 years in
sales/marketing/business development responsibility. Excellent
communication skills, good analytical business, computer and
presentation skills are essential.</p>
<p>Candidates should have a nursing qualification or university
degree in life science or Business Studies.</p>
