</ul>
<p>The following vacancy has arisen in the Maidenhead office:</p>
<h2><a name="Clinical Quality Assurance Auditor">Clinical Quality
Assurance Auditor</a></h2>
<p>We are looking for a Clinical Quality Assurance Auditor to
audit investigator sites throughout Europe, to conduct audits in
Business Units in Maidenhead and support training of staff. All
work will be to GCP.ISO9001 and Corning Besselaar standards.</p>
<p>Candidates will have a biological background, and will have
specific experience within the clinical trial process. Ideally,
we are seeking candidates with a nursing background or Life
Sciences graduate. An awareness of GCP and/or IS09000 is
essential, although extensive training will be given.</p>
<p>The candidate requires good numeracy, have excellent
interpersonal skills and will have the motivation to succeed in
the appointment. Attention to detail is essential for any
candidate applying for this appointment. They should have a
willingness to travel and be able to drive a car.</p>
<p>&#160; </p>
<p>If you are interested in joining our rapidly expanding
organisation, please forward your Curriculum Vitae to:</p>
