<html>
<head>
<title>Process Validation:Appendix 2</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
link="#000080">
<h4 align="center"><img src="IMAGES/home.gif" align="bottom"
width="104" height="38"></h4>
<h4 align="center"><img src="images/cps2.gif" align="bottom"
width="306" height="45"></h4>
<h4>A Guide to Process Validation for Pharmaceuticals Produced in
Mammalian Cell Culture </h4>
<h1>APPENDIX 2 </h1>
<h2>Example of cytotoxicity and viral interference assays </h2>
<h4>Cytotoxicity assay </h4>
<p>The test solution used in the process was serially diluted and
inoculated onto vero cell monolayers. These were then incubated
and observed for toxic effects. </p>
<table border="1" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td> 
        <h4 align="center">Solution </h4>
        </td>
        <td> 
        <h4 align="center">Appearance of indicator cells </h4>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Growth medium (control)</td>
        <td>Normal</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Neat test solution</td>
        <td>Cytotoxic</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Test solution diluted 1 in 10</td>
        <td>Normal</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Test solution diluted 1 in 100</td>
        <td>Normal</td>
    </tr>
</table>
<h4>Viral interference </h4>
<p>The test solution was serial diluted and added to monolayers
of vero cells. Twenty plaque forming units of poliovirus were
added to each monolayer. After one hour incubation the
supernatant was removed and replaced with medium. The number of
plaques recorded on plates with test solution was compared to the
number recorded on plates in medium. </p>
<table border="1" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td> 
        <h4 align="center">Solution </h4>
        </td>
        <td> 
        <h4 align="center">Average number of plaques per plate </h4>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Growth medium (control)</td>
        <td>20</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Test solution 1 in 10</td>
        <td>12</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Test solution 1 in 100</td>
        <td>21</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Test solution 1 in 20</td>
        <td>20</td>
    </tr>
</table>
<h4>Conclusion </h4>
<p>A 1 in 10 dilution of test solution is non-cytotoxic, but
interferes with the ability of polio to infect vero cells. Hence
in the process, the test solution/virus mixture was diluted 1 in
100 before assay. </p>
<p align="center">&#160;</p>
<table width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td width="50%"> 
        <p align="right"><img src="IMAGES/th_up.gif"
        align="bottom" width="25" height="19"> <a
        href="procindx.htm">Return to Contents</a> </p>
        </td>
        <td width="50%"> 
        <p align="left"><img src="IMAGES/r_hand.gif"
        align="bottom" width="33" height="14"><a
        href="procva10.htm"> Next page</a></p>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
