<html>

<head>
<title>Defining The Products</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body background="IMAGES/backgrnd.gif">
<h1>Defining The Products</h1>
<h2>Defining The Products</h2>
<h2>BIOPHARMACEUTICALS - Products of a zoological origin intended for in vivo use in man or 
animals</h2>
<h2>Conventional</h2>
<ul>
<li>Live animals - eg, vaccines</li>
<li>Tissue culture - eg, vaccines, cytokines and antibodies</li>
<li>Products from blood and solid tissues - eg, clotting factors, cytokines and hormones</li>
</ul>
<h2>Biotechnology</h2>
<ul>
<li>Hybridomas - monoclonal antibodies</li>
<li>rDNA technology - all classes</li>
<li>Gene therapy vectors</li>
</ul>
<table>
<tr><td width=100 HEIGHT="100"><a href="tsld002.htm">Previous slide </a></td><td width=100 HEIGHT="100"><a href="tsld004.htm">Next slide </a></td><td width=150 HEIGHT="100"><a href="pptindex.htm">Back to the first slide </a></td><td width=150 HEIGHT="100"><a href="sld003.htm">View Graphic Version </a></td></tr>
</table>
