<html>

<head>
<title>The Need for Safety Testing</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body background="IMAGES/backgrnd.gif">
<h1>The Need for Safety Testing</h1>
<h2>The Need for Safety Testing</h2>
<h2>HISTORICAL</h2>
<ul>
<li>Viral contamination of the host</li>
<li>SV40 virus in polio vaccines produced in Rhesus monkey kidney cell cultures</li>
<li>Avian leukosis virus in yellow fever vaccines produced in hen's eggs</li>
<li>HIV, HTLV, Hepatitis A, B and C and other viruses in blood and blood products</li>
<li>The presence of Creutzfeld-Jacob agent in extracts of pituitary gland from human cadavers</li>
<li>The presence of Hepatitis B in serum stabiliser during lyophilization of yellow fever vaccines</li>
</ul>
<h2>THE FUTURE</h2>
<ul>
<li>Contamination from unexpected sources ?</li>
</ul>
<table>
<tr><td width=100 HEIGHT="100"><a href="tsld005.htm">Previous slide </a></td><td width=100 HEIGHT="100"><a href="tsld007.htm">Next slide </a></td><td width=150 HEIGHT="100"><a href="pptindex.htm">Back to the first slide </a></td><td width=150 HEIGHT="100"><a href="sld006.htm">View Graphic Version </a></td></tr>
</table>
