<title>Two Major Safety Concerns</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body background="IMAGES/backgrnd.gif">
<h1>Two Major Safety Concerns</h1>
<h2>Two Major Safety Concerns</h2>
<h2>Contamination</h2>
<ul>
<li>Retroviruses</li>
<li>Adventitious viruses</li>
<li>Mycoplasma</li>
<li>Bacteria &amp; fungi</li>
<li>DNA</li>
</ul>
<h2>Other macromolecules</h2>
<h2>Toxicity of the final product</h2>
<ul>
<li>General toxicity</li>
<li>Receptor-mediated toxicity</li>
</ul>
