<html>

<head>
<title>Philosophy of Approach</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body background="IMAGES/backgrnd.gif">
<h1>Philosophy of Approach</h1>
<h2>Philosophy of Approach</h2>
<ul>
<li>Ensure all starting materials, including biological additives, are free from adventitious agents</li>
<li>Validate purification processes for clearance of adventitious agents and &quot;acceptable&quot; endogenous ones</li>
<li>Monitor batches</li>
</ul>
<table>
<tr><td width=100 HEIGHT="100"><a href="tsld007.htm">Previous slide </a></td><td width=100 HEIGHT="100"><a href="tsld009.htm">Next slide </a></td><td width=150 HEIGHT="100"><a href="pptindex.htm">Back to the first slide </a></td><td width=150 HEIGHT="100"><a href="sld008.htm">View Graphic Version </a></td></tr>
</table>
<p><br>
</p>
</body>

