<head>
<title>Sources of Contamination - MCB</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
link="#000080">
<h1>Sources of Contamination - MCB</h1>
<h2>Sources of Contamination - MCB</h2>
<h2>Endogenous viruses</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Proviruses - retroviruses</li>
    <li>Latent viruses - herpes</li>
</ul>
<h2>Adventitious viruses</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Cell line from infected donor</li>
    <li>Infected biological additives - serum, insulin</li>
    <li>Accidental exogenous contamination during handling</li>
</ul>
