<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//IETF//DTD HTML//EN">

<html>

<head>
<title>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body background="IMAGES/backgrnd.gif">
<h1>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h1>
<h2>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h2>
<h2>MCB - Test Thoroughly - source of all product</h2>
<ul>
<li>Test for contaminants - virus, retrovirus, mycoplasma, bacteria, and fungi</li>
<li>Characterise genetic content and use as baseline</li>
</ul>
<h2>WCB - No requirement to test </h2>
<ul>
<li>(Unless to be regarded as MCB)</li>
</ul>
<h2>MEPC - Test thoroughly</h2>
<ul>
<li>Test for contaminants especially latent viruses or pro-viruses</li>
<li>Characterise genetic content and compare with MCB data</li>
</ul>
<h2>Additives</h2>
<ul>
<li>Test each batch for adventitious agents relevant to the species of origin</li>
</ul>
<h2>Overview</h2>
<table>
<tr><td width=100 HEIGHT="100"><a href="tsld010.htm">Previous slide </a></td><td width=100 HEIGHT="100"><a href="tsld013.htm">Next slide </a></td><td width=150 HEIGHT="100"><a href="pptindex.htm">Back to the first slide </a></td><td width=150 HEIGHT="100"><a href="sld012.htm">View Graphic Version </a></td></tr>
</table>
<p><br>
</p>
</body>

</html>
