<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3O/DTD HTML//EN">

<html>
<head>
<title>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
link="#000080">
<h1>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h1>
<h2>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Use &quot;catch all&quot; screening assays to detect:-
        <ul>
            <li>Wide range of viruses known to infect producer
                cell line</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
            <li>Use specific assays to detect:-
                <ul>
                    <li>Highly pathogenic viruses of particular
                        concern</li>
                    <li>Slow growing viruses</li>
                    <li>Latent viruses</li>
                    <li>DNA proviruses (retroviruses)</li>
                </ul>
                <h2>Overview </h2>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <td width="100" height="100"><a
                        href="tsld012.htm">Previous slide </a></td>
                        <td width="100" height="100"><a
