<body background="images/backgrnd.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
link="#000080">
<h1>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h1>
<h2>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h2>
<h2>Effect in cell culture </h2>
<ul>
    <li>Use relevant indicator lines
        <ul>
            <li>Choice determined by producer cell line and
                additive donor species</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
            <li>Monitor status of cell sheet over extended period
                <ul>
                    <li>cpe - type determined by cell line and
                        virus type being monitored</li>
                    <li>Haemadsorption, haemagglutination</li>
                </ul>
                <ul>
                    <li>Passage supernatant onto fresh cells</li>
                    <li>Include specific immuno-probes for slow
                        growing viruses and non cpe forming
                        viruses </li>
                </ul>
                <h2>&quot;Catch all&quot; screening assays -
                Adventitious viruses </h2>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <td width="100" height="100"><a
                        href="tsld013.htm">Previous slide </a></td>
                        <td width="100" height="100"><a
                        href="tsld015.htm">Next slide </a></td>
