link="#000080">
<h1>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h1>
<h2>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h2>
<h2>Effect in animals and eggs</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Use relevant animal species
        <ul>
            <li>Choice determined by producer cell line and
                additive donor species </li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
            <li>Use multiple injection sites</li>
            <li>Monitor status of test species over extended
                period
                <ul>
                    <li>General well-being and specific
                        indicators of viral infection</li>
                    <li>Haemadsorption, haemagglutination in egg
                        fluids</li>
                </ul>
                <ul>
                    <li>In new-born mice, passage homogenised
                        tissue into further animals</li>
                </ul>
                <h2>&quot;Catch all&quot; screening assays -
                Adventitious viruses </h2>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <td width="100" height="100"><a
