link="#000080">
<h1>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h1>
<h2>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h2>
<h2>Antibody production in relevant species</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Used for rodent viruses</li>
</ul>
<h2>PCR and/or hybridisation</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Extremely sensitive</li>
    <li>Use multiple primer pairs for high specificity</li>
    <li>No information regarding infectivity</li>
</ul>
<h2>Immunological probe</h2>
<ul>
    <li>For viral antigens or for antibodies</li>
</ul>
<h2>Specific assays - Adventitious viruses</h2>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td width="100" height="100"><a href="tsld015.htm">Previous
