<html>
<head>
<title>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
link="#000080">
<h1>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h1>
<h2>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h2>
<h2>Transmission EM</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Will differentiate between A, B, C and D type
        retroviruses</li>
    <li>No information on infectivity</li>
    <li>Around 500,000 fold less sensitive than infectivity
        assays</li>
    <li>Also detects adventitious viruses</li>
</ul>
<h2>Reverse transcriptase</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Differentiates between C and D type</li>
    <li>No information on infectivity</li>
    <li>Around 1000 fold less sensitive than infectivity assays</li>
</ul>
<h2>&quot;Catch all&quot; screening assays - Retroviruses</h2>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td width="100" height="100"><a href="tsld016.htm">Previous
        slide </a></td>
        <td width="100" height="100"><a href="tsld018.htm">Next
        slide </a></td>
        <td width="150" height="100"><a href="pptindex.htm">Back
        to the first slide </a></td>
        <td width="150" height="100"><a href="sld017.htm">View
        Graphic Version </a></td>
    </tr>
</table>
