<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3O/DTD HTML//EN">

<html>
<head>
<title>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
link="#000080">
<h1>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h1>
<h2>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h2>
<h2>Cell culture infectivity assays</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Indicator cell specific</li>
    <li>Monitor status of cell sheet for cpe over extended period</li>
    <li>Include specific immuno-probes for slow growing viruses</li>
    <li>Very sensitive </li>
</ul>
<h2>PCR for provirus or RT PCR for RNA virus</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Extremely sensitive</li>
    <li>Use multiple primer pairs for high specificity</li>
    <li>No information regarding infectivity</li>
</ul>
<h2>Immunoassay</h2>
<ul>
    <li>For viral antigens or for antibodies</li>
</ul>
<h2>Specific assays - Retroviruses</h2>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td width="100" height="100"><a href="tsld017.htm">Previous
        slide </a></td>
        <td width="100" height="100"><a href="tsld019.htm">Next
        slide </a></td>
        <td width="150" height="100"><a href="pptindex.htm">Back
        to the first slide </a></td>
        <td width="150" height="100"><a href="sld018.htm">View
        Graphic Version </a></td>
    </tr>
