<head>
<title>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
link="#000080">
<h1>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h1>
<h2>Cell Bank and Additive Testing</h2>
<h2>Genetic characterisation</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Cytogenetic analysis - Karyology with giemsa banding and
        chromosomal aberration measurement</li>
    <li>Gene sequence (or mRNA) and product sequence</li>
    <li>DNA fingerprinting</li>
    <li>Isoenzyme analysis</li>
</ul>
<h2>Bacteria and fungi</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Growth on special media - including TC for mycoplasma</li>
    <li>Scanning EM</li>
</ul>
<h2>General</h2>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td width="100" height="100"><a href="tsld018.htm">Previous
        slide </a></td>
