<html>
<head>
<title>Process Validation</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
link="#000080">
<h1>Process Validation</h1>
<h2>Process Validation</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Discuss design of validation studies as part of overall
        strategic plan</li>
    <li>Incorporate the need to remove virus in the design stage</li>
    <li>Carry out cytotoxicity studies prior to validation</li>
    <li>Consider implications of using affinity columns late in
        process</li>
    <li>Changes in process:
        <ul>
            <li>Require re-validation of changed and subsequent
                steps</li>
            <li>Require repeats of studies done (eg, tox) on
                final product</li>
            <li>Are potentially very expensive</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
<h2>Early Planning</h2>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td width="100" height="100"><a href="tsld022.htm">Previous
        slide </a></td>
        <td width="100" height="100"><a href="tsld024.htm">Next
        slide </a></td>
        <td width="150" height="100"><a href="pptindex.htm">Back
        to the first slide </a></td>
        <td width="150" height="100"><a href="sld023.htm">View
        Graphic Version </a></td>
    </tr>
</table>
