<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3O/DTD HTML//EN">

<html>
<head>
<title>Process Validation</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
link="#000080">
<h1>Process Validation</h1>
<h2>Process Validation</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Selection should include large, small, enveloped and
        non-enveloped. Use DNA and RNA viruses with stages which
        interact with nucleic acids</li>
    <li>Relevant viruses - can infect producer cell line</li>
    <li>Model viruses - resistant, difficult to remove. Use of
        these viruses imparts confidence that process can deal
        with the unexpected</li>
</ul>
<h2>Choice of Virus</h2>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td width="100" height="100"><a href="tsld023.htm">Previous
        slide </a></td>
        <td width="100" height="100"><a href="tsld025.htm">Next
