<title>Process Validation</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
link="#000080">
<h1>Process Validation</h1>
<h2>Process Validation</h2>
<h2>Necessary to show greater reduction than highest likely
contaminant titre to take account of:</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Discrepancies in scale-down
        <ul>
            <li>Changes in relative product / impurity elution</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
            <li>Breakdown of column integrity due to re-use
                <ul>
                    <li>Changes in charge</li>
                    <li>Changes in particle size</li>
                    <li>Channelisation</li>
                </ul>
                <h2>Safety Margin </h2>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <td width="100" height="100"><a
                        href="tsld024.htm">Previous slide </a></td>
                        <td width="100" height="100"><a
                        href="tsld028.htm">Next slide </a></td>
                        <td width="150" height="100"><a
                        href="pptindex.htm">Back to the first
                        slide </a></td>
                        <td width="150" height="100"><a
                        href="sld025.htm">View Graphic Version </a></td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
                <p>&#160;</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
</body>
