<h1>Process Validation</h1>
<h2>Process Validation</h2>
<h2>Virus killing or removal often does not follow first order
kinetics due to the presence of a &quot;resistant&quot;
sub-population. </h2>
<ul>
    <li>Validate purification stages which have different
        physicochemical parameters
        <ul>
            <li>Allows multiplication of overall log reductions
                in titre</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Mode of Action </h2>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <td width="100" height="100"><a
                href="tsld025.htm">Previous slide </a></td>
