<html>
<head>
<title>Process Validation</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
link="#000080">
<h1>Process Validation</h1>
<h2>Process Validation</h2>
<h2>Regulatory Authorities wish to see evidence of the fate of
removed virus. To achieve this:</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Virus retained on column
        <ul>
            <li>Show lethality of regeneration buffers</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
            <li>Virus eluted but separated from product
                <ul>
                    <li>Check other fractions for virus titre</li>
                    <li>Especially check fractions either side of
                        product peak - provides confidence of
                        adequate separation</li>
                </ul>
                <h2>Fate of Virus </h2>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <td width="100" height="100"><a
                        href="sld027.htm">Previous slide </a></td>
                        <td width="100" height="100"><a
                        href="tsld029.htm">Next slide </a></td>
                        <td width="150" height="100"><a
                        href="pptindex.htm">Back to the first
                        slide </a></td>
                        <td width="150" height="100"><a
                        href="sld028.htm">View Graphic Version </a></td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
                <p>&#160; </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
</body>
</html>
