<h1>Process Validation</h1>
<h2>Process Validation</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Plaque or focus assays preferable to TCID50</li>
    <li>Unpredictable effect of freezing samples prior to assay</li>
    <li>Adequate controls must be incorporated</li>
    <li>Authorities in Europe increasingly concerned as to
        application of statistical considerations to results</li>
</ul>
