<html>
<head>
<title>Pre-Clinical Safety Testing Initial Considerations</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
link="#000080">
<h1>Pre-Clinical Safety Testing Initial Considerations</h1>
<h2>Pre-Clinical Safety Testing Initial Considerations</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Category 
        <ul>
            <li>Vaccine</li>
            <li>Monoclonal antibody</li>
            <li>Cytokine .....etc</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Physicochemical nature 
        <ul>
            <li>Nature identical, similar, unrelated</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
<ul>
    <li>Pattern of clinical use 
        <ul>
            <li>Replacement therapy (low dose)</li>
            <li>High dose</li>
            <li>Single or repeat dose</li>
            <li>Patient population</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Dynamic evaluation 
        <ul>
            <li>Repeatedly revise strategy in light of results</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
<h2>Develop a customised strategy on a case-by-case basis,
approach dictated by:</h2>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td width="100" height="100"><a href="sld035.htm">Previous
        slide </a></td>
        <td width="100" height="100"><a href="tsld037.htm">Next
        slide </a></td>
        <td width="150" height="100"><a href="pptindex.htm">Back
        to the first slide </a></td>
        <td width="150" height="100"><a href="sld036.htm">View
        Graphic Version </a></td>
    </tr>
</table>
<p>&#160;</p>
