<h1>Species Selection</h1>
<h2>Species Selection</h2>
<h2>Central issue is selection of species. Need to consider:</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Immunological response</li>
    <li>Pharmacological activity</li>
    <li>Pharmacokinetic data</li>
</ul>
<h2>Results are interelated and best approach may be to carry out
preliminary small-scale studies</h2>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td width="100" height="100"><a href="tsld036.htm">Previous
        slide </a></td>
        <td width="100" height="100"><a href="tsld038.htm">Next
