<h1>Dose Selection</h1>
<h2>Dose Selection</h2>
<h2>Need to consider:</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Intended clinical usage
        <ul>
            <li>Single or repeat dosing</li>
            <li>Replacement therapy or high doses</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
            <li>Immunological response</li>
            <li>Pharmacological activity</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Again results are interelated </h2>
