<h1><u>Summary</u></h1>
<h2>Summary</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Contaminant testing - Two &quot;pronged&quot; approach
        <ul>
            <li>Cell bank and additive testing</li>
            <li>Process validation </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Toxicity testing - Do not do irrelevant tests, choose
        dose and species wisely
        <ul>
            <li>Pharmacodynamic studies</li>
            <li>Pharmacokinetic studies</li>
            <li>Toxicity studies</li>
            <li>Develop specific assays where indicated</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
