<h1><u>Information Innovation and Technology</u></h1>
<p><a href="cps.htm">Corning Pharmaceutical Services</a> and
Corning Besselaar are leaders in the development of client
information technology.We utilize powerful state-of-the-art
information programs and systems, many of which are registered
under propriety patents and specially designed to meet the most
challenging data and information requirements a project can
demand. These highly specialized systems and programs are
invaluable in facilitating the successful and timely development
of your product. </p>
<p>We use our unique data management systems to continually
