http://www.savers.org:80/savers/quotes.html 204.71.237.73 19970107213105 text/html 6688
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 07-Jan-97 21:31:09 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 22-Oct-96 15:32:14 GMT
Content-length: 6503
