<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/savers/about.html 204.71.237.73 19970107214755 text/html 9849
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 07-Jan-97 21:47:34 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 05-Mar-96 20:25:57 GMT
