<html>
<head><title>Savers & Investors League Web Site</title></head>
<body link="#2F4F2F" vlink="#3232CD" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<!--<body background="/savers/images/sandston.gif">-->
<img src="/counting/sil/count.gif">    
<center>
<img src ="/savers/images/griffgrn.gif" alt=""><br>
<img src="/savers/images/legendwh.gif" alt=""><br>
<img src="/savers/images/boxloggr.gif" alt="SAVERS &amp; INVESTORS LEAGUE"><br>
<p>
<font size=4><b><i>Working for the Common Sense Taxation<br>
of Personal Savings and Investments</font></i></b>
<p>
<img src="/savers/images/smgrnln1.gif"><br>
 <p>
<font size=4>Join the League On-Line<br>
and be automatically entered in our weekly drawing for a<br>
free Savers &amp; Investors League T-shirt!<br>

</font>
<i>No Membership Fee Required</i><br>
<a href="/savers/guestbook.html">On-Line Form</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="https://secure.townhall.com/savers/savers-sec.html">Secure On-Line Form</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="/savers/form.html">Hard Copy Form</a><br>
<p>
<img src="/savers/images/smgrnln1.gif"><br>
<p>
<table border=3 cellpadding=5 cellspacing=2>
<tr align=center>
<td>
<font size=4>Learn About...</font><br>
<font size=5 color="#2F4F2F">Individual Investment Accounts<br>
(IIAs)<br>
</font>
</tr>
</table>
<p>
</center>
<img src="/savers/images/smgrndot.gif"> What Are They? Get a <a href="/savers/legislation/iiasumm.html">Snapshot View</a> of this exciting legislation.<br>
<p>
<img src="/savers/images/smgrndot.gif"> Read and Review the actual legislation as introduced in the 104th Congress:<br>
<ul>
<li> <a href="/savers/legislation/hr328.html">H.R. 328</a><br>
<li> <a href="/savers/legislation/s159.html">S. 159</a><br>
</ul>
<p>
<img src="/savers/images/smgrndot.gif"> Read the &quot;Dear Colleague&quot; Letters written and sent by the Bill Sponsors<br>
<ul>
<li> <a href="/savers/library/mccrery.html">Representative Jim McCrery</a> (R-LA) House Ways &amp; Means Committee<br>
<li> <a href="/savers/library/breaux.html">Senator John Breaux</a> (D-LA) Senate Finance Committee<br>
</ul>
