  <TD width="220" valign="top"><center>
<b> Tuesday, January 07 1997
 </b>
<p> What's Wrong With<br> This Picture?<br>
  <hr width="55%" size="3">
  <img src="/townhall/scripts/abic.cgi" height="336" width="176" ALT="An UnRepresentative"></center><p>
  <font size="-1">Visit ABIC's web site again and again to meet other members of Congress who are un-representative of the people.
</font>
  </TD>
  <TD valign="top" align="center">
  <p align="right">
<i>
"The second feature I dislike (about the new
U.S. Constitution) and greatly dislike, is the abandonment in every
instance of the necessity of rotation in office..."<br>
<b>  Thomas Jefferson to
Madison, December 20, 1787

</font></b></i>
