<p>Read installment 2 of <i>Setting Limits</i> documenting
the travesties committed by our 
<a href="/abic/welfare.html.cgi">Congressional Welfare Kings & Queens</a>
<p>Read the third installment of <i>Setting Limits</i> exposing 
our <a href="/abic/unrep.html.cgi">Un-Representatives</a>
 opposition to the will of the people 
<p>Read the fourth installment of <i>Setting Limits</i> about how the <a href="/abic/decoys.html.cgi">Hatfield and Decoys</a> opposed the Balanced Budget Bill.
<p>Read the fifth installment of <i>Setting Limits</i> which describes who <a href="/abic/antagon.html.cgi">The Antagonists</a> are in the balanced budget and term limit battles.
<p>The sixth installment of <i>Setting Limits</i> displays The Good Guys and The Bad Guys:
<a href="/abic/ggbg.html.cgi">The "EZ" Reference Guide to the House Term Limits Vote</a>
<p>
<h5>ABIC will make a new chapter available online 
periodically.</h5> 
<p>
</blockquote>
